- Flight F3606586 departing Chicago at 13:15 and arriving in Atlanta at 13:54, with a duration of 1 hour and 39 minutes, priced at $221.
- Flight F3509453 departing Chicago at 15:40 and arriving in Atlanta at 16:55, with a duration of 2 hours and 15 minutes, priced at $258.
- Flight F3528439 departing Chicago at 18:32 and arriving in Atlanta at 19:31, with a duration of 1 hour and 59 minutes, priced at $254.

Please note that prices and availability may vary, and you should book your flights and accommodations as soon as possible to secure the best deals.

I hope this plan meets your expectations and helps you have a fantastic trip to Chicago!

